      "amount": "1/4 teaspoon"
    },
    {
      "name": "Toasted sesame seeds",
      "amount": "1 tablespoon"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "In a large mortar and pestle, pound the garlic and ginger until well combined and fragrant.",
    "Add the Korean greens to the mortar and pestle and pound until they are well bruised and fragrant.",
    "Add the bouquet garni to the mortar and pestle and pound until the greens are well coated with the herbs.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together the sesame oil, rice vinegar, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Pour the dressing over the greens and toss to combine.",
    "Sprinkle the toasted sesame seeds over the top of the muchim and serve.",
    "Garnish with additional herbs if desired.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy."
  ],
